description:
Bloomberg Markets with Carol Massar and Cory Johnson. GUEST: Anne Mostue Bloomberg Reporter Bloomberg News Co-host of Bloomberg Bay State Business Hour Discussing the trend of med students going from graduating medical school straight into business rather than practicing medicine.
